Download TIGER shapes for Elementary School Districts

Source: R/elementary_school_districts.R
tt_elementary_school_districts.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Elementary School Districts

Usage

tt_elementary_school_districts(state, year = 2021)

Arguments

state

FIPs, postal codes, or full name of states.

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_elementary_school_districts('AZ')
